<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>In groups, the sustained dps of a good mage parsed has been around 300-400. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Or wizard <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
