Seems that we really shouldn't be all that worried about other classes abilities. More to the point, we should be worried about our own abilities. Manaburn being reinstated as it was, with a 15 sec timer instead of a minute (one can grumble about the amount of time, but a minute is too much). Exodus, should be lowered substantially in the recharge time, even at 50 minutes with AA lowering the recharge time, is too long. Something more along the lines of 30 minutes with AA. People love the 1/10 of a second cast time. It's the basic get out of jail free card.<br>
