<br>
Because BoT is the only place this spell really works, it is VERY crowded on our server. Most weekends I can't find a camp open unless I log on before 6am.<br>
<br>
Even with taking many precaustions and being very skilled I die alot with this spell. Charm seems to break most often when your fighting stuff, which means mage normally dies. When my wife and I don't use charm, we can pull non-stop without danger. The exp is still faster with pet, over a period of hours, but not by as much as you'd imagine and the increase in danger is probably more than 20 times. <br>
<br>
In any raid outside of BoT my wizard will do 2-3x the dmg. Being lvl 65 wizard with SoS, really makes playing a wizard fun again.<br>
<br>
It's a great spell while in BoT, when it works right, when it doesn't (seems like 4 out of 5 times it doesn't), well you get good a meming your spells and medding.<br>
